{"tid":2365444,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"民主黨 : 就算民主黨全被DQ都應派人參選，強調絕不主動放棄立法會陣地 !","createTime":"2021-01-13T18:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T21:31:33.000Z","uid":219007,"like":4,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"22a48c680f09af9e5537bb41b9de023d0fcce37b","tid":2365444,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T18:52:43.000Z","msg":"HK01 2021-01-11 07:00<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210110/425058126924877824701435.jpeg/f_SF8qz9uG5qBcP_ncHioKLXFMBrjQG7kccH8JHHB_A?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210110%2F425058126924877824701435.jpeg%2Ff_SF8qz9uG5qBcP_ncHioKLXFMBrjQG7kccH8JHHB_A%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=cc54b327&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港區國安法實施半年，多次「出鞘亮刃」，港府上周更首次以涉嫌「顛覆國家政權罪」大舉拘捕55名參與民主派初選人士，成為回歸後對民主派的最大型行動。<br />\n<br />\n是次事件中，民主黨七名前立法會議員亦全部涉案。面對如此局勢，上月剛成為民主黨副主席的梁翊婷直言，認為未來環境可能更差，但就算絕無機會取得立法會過半數議席取得主導權，她亦認為不能放棄立法會的陣地，就算民主黨全員被DQ，只餘下「一個叔叔，一個姨姨」都應派人參選，爭取民意授權，強調絕不主動放棄。<br />\n<br />\n國安法下民主派危機四伏，四大罪項還包括勾結外國勢力，而民主黨國際事務委員會正是本港政界就「BNO平權」與英國政界關係最顯眼的角色之一。身為委員的梁翊婷強調，會在國安法下繼續做自覺絕對沒錯的工作，強調一直只是向英方反映港人疑難，而BNO更是港人長久以來擁有的權利，無理由因為英方擴充有關福利，就煞停民主黨有關工作。"},{"pid":"fea5683c793b693993af1d3eee8ccfbb1ea175e0","tid":2365444,"uid":206080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T19:33:54.000Z","msg":"未開始已經結束你啦共產黨"},{"pid":"c6d880b2a076931ee9922a7848ae6b6ec9032298","tid":2365444,"uid":115579,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T19:39:46.000Z","msg":"入得泛民嘅我估都重視立法會，人各有志，但而家係選都唔俾你選，俾你選到又下下紅牌你"},{"pid":"99c915222b206fce14b998603b2f67d97f0124b5","tid":2365444,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T19:40:41.000Z","msg":"被dq師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"665440751ddfd68f8eebc6473afc557464bd1a90","tid":2365444,"uid":743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T19:41:39.000Z","msg":"比返你拎23席<br />\n啱啱好 1/3 都唔夠 當養狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0585ddb06ebaebe05df0f50573765cfd3eaea6a6","tid":2365444,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T19:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2021/01/14/035236_6e34030cba660235e7e5b29df88a080f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2021%2F01%2F14%2F035236_6e34030cba660235e7e5b29df88a080f.jpg&h=fd19eb66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同共產黨傾掂數做花瓶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b76ee88912dae4be123e322f3f50378c3128accb","tid":2365444,"uid":77547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T19:53:56.000Z","msg":"呢個位注定兩面不討好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 類比返日治時間就明"},{"pid":"e334332a26e44cbedf291303edfb808fe443d672","tid":2365444,"uid":275225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T20:04:14.000Z","msg":"中國特色民主黨<br />\n報名當爭取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed526295beffc94579c28b2f0d3848f372148a7d","tid":2365444,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T20:19:33.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2469504704f2a587209a0226251d018a65e4578b","tid":2365444,"uid":189430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T20:22:41.000Z","msg":"弱智"},{"pid":"3aebfe8d5d44a744075aaadc5bad5719560fd91f","tid":2365444,"uid":15084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T20:25:59.000Z","msg":"醒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36cd09ada38717